Directions\
Chop the chocolate and place it in a heat-proof bowl set over a pan of simmering water.\
Add the cream, zest, coffee, and liqueur and stir constantly until the chocolate is melted and smooth.\
Transfer the mixture to a fondue pot and serve warm with pound cake, doughnuts, long-stemmed strawberries, bananas or pretzels.\
